          <h1>Hangwoo Cho</h1>
          <p class="about-simple__bio">Software Solution Engineer focused on practical AI / ML systems.</p>

          <dl class="about-simple__meta">
            <div>
              <dt>GitHub</dt>
              <dd>
                <a href="https://github.com/wedding-crasher" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">@wedding-crasher</a>
              </dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt>LinkedIn</dt>
              <dd>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/hangwoo-cho-01257a252" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">hangwoo-cho-01257a252</a>
              </dd>
